{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779039288989,"sessionID":"ses_1c900d483ffe3X7x4o8qKel0y4","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_fe6d59f006d8ea15","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/pruiz/Develop/mine/CodeCome-e2e-testing/itemdb/notes/execution-model.md","content":"# Execution Model\n\n## Overview\n\nThe target is a standalone CLI executable with no persistent runtime. It processes command-line arguments and exits.\n\n## Entrypoint\n\n- **Binary**: `bin/sample-c-cli`\n- **Entry function**: `main()` in `src/main.c`\n\n## Runtime Invocation\n\n```bash\n./bin/sample-c-cli [--help|greet <name>|echo <message>|remove <path>]\n```\n\n## Commands\n\n### Help\n\n```bash\n./bin/sample-c-cli --help\n```\n\nPrints help text and exits.\n\n### Greet\n\n```bash\n./bin/sample-c-cli greet <name>\n```\n\nPrints \"Hello, <name>\" to stdout.\n\n**Example**: `./bin/sample-c-cli greet Alice` outputs `Hello, Alice`\n\n### Echo\n\n```bash\n./bin/sample-c-cli echo <message>\n```\n\nPrints the message to stdout.\n\n**Example**: `./bin/sample-c-cli echo hello` outputs `hello`\n\n### Remove\n\n```bash\n./bin/sample-c-cli remove <path>\n```\n\nExecutes `rm -f <path>` via shell.\n\n**Example**: `./bin/sample-c-cli remove /tmp/testfile` deletes the file\n\n## Runtime Dependencies\n\n- **None** — Pure C with standard library only\n- No database, no network, no external services\n\n## Configuration Files\n\n- **None** — No configuration files used\n\n## Environment Variables\n\n- **None** — No environment variables affect behavior\n\n## Ports\n\n- **None** — No network ports used\n\n## Test Harness\n\nThe test script `tests/smoke.sh` runs:\n\n```bash\n./bin/sample-c-cli --help >/dev/null\n./bin/sample-c-cli greet tester >/dev/null\n./bin/sample-c-cli echo hello >/dev/null\n```\n\n## Runtime Model Summary\n\n| Aspect | Value |\n|--------|-------|\n| Type | CLI executable |\n| Persistence | None — one-shot execution |\n| User session | None |\n| State | Stateless |\n| Network | None |"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/pruiz/Develop/mine/CodeCome-e2e-testing/itemdb/notes/execution-model.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"itemdb/notes/execution-model.md","time":{"start":1779039288982,"end":1779039288988}},"id":"prt_e37013e93001cFnHj1OIUQn74u","sessionID":"ses_1c900d483ffe3X7x4o8qKel0y4","messageID":"msg_e3700e0ac001ZUd5Ky0l65WEgV"}}
